com.isoterik.mgdx

Class MinGdx

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.isoterik.mgdx.MinGdx

  • public final class MinGdx
extends java.lang.Object
    Environment class holding references to Application, Graphics, GameAssetsLoader, SceneManager and AudioManager instances. The references are held in public final fields which allows access to all sub systems. Use instance() to get the shared instance.
